   <Ritual>
      <Nerangs id="ritualNerangs">
         <ab>VVrS38.12 Var. a (mss. 4010, 4025, 4030a, 4040, 4063):</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            ... <em>īšanąm drujəm</em> ēn gyāg hōm ud urwarām kōftan ud hāwan škāftan ud zōhr andar kardan andar hōm pālā kardan</ab> 
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            "... <em>īšanąm drujəm</em>. At this passage, he should strike the <em>hōm</em> and <em>urwarām</em> and hit the <em>hāwan</em> and pour <em>zōhr</em> in them
            and throw (the mix) into the <em>hōm pālā</em>."</ab>
         
         <ab>VVrS38.12 Var. c (ms. 4050):</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            ... <em>īšanąm drujəm</em> ēn gyāg hōm ud urwarām kōftan ud hāwan škāftan</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            "... <em>īšanąm drujəm</em>. At this passage, he should strike the <em>hōm</em> and <em>urwarām</em> and hit the <em>hāwan</em>."</ab>
      </Nerangs>
   </Ritual>
